人類腸道細胞致病性病毒: ECHO virus，enteric cytopathic human orphan virus

傳染性造血器官壞死症（魚）: Columbia River sockeye salmon disease，infectious hematopoietie necrosis

雞白血病補體結合反應試驗: COFAL test，Complement-Fixation test for Avian Leukosis virus

雞胚致死孤兒病毒素: CELO virus，chicken embryo lethal orphan virus

小型貝爾茨雜爾白火雞: Beltsville No. 1 swine Small White turkey

蒼白軟濕肉症候群，水花肉綜合症: PSE syndrome，pale soft  exudative pork syndrome
